UPDATE/ CORRECTION
I’ve come to regret how I depicted Berserks director Shin Itagaki in this video. I don’t know what happened during the production of this series, and blaming it on the contributions of a single person is an irresponsible and damaging statement to make. I apologize to Itagaki, and for the potential misinformation spread. I will do my best to do better in the future.
